The paper discusses the design of an auction mechanism, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and mechanism design (cs.EC). The use of quantized bids involves discretization, which is a topic in data structures (cs.DS) and information theory (cs.IT). The design of the auction mechanism also involves optimizing the utility of the seller, which can be achieved through artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques.
